          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 1 poin <span style=\"color: #99FFFF\">Cryo DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/14/15595270/464df75643b85d808ea7457d333c2520_8281857339808793362.png",
                "id": "talent31472",
                "key": "Cool-Color Capture",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Cool-Color Capture"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 1 poin <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo DMG</span>.</p><p>Memberikan <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Snappy Silhouette</span> kepada target.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Snappy Silhouette</span></strong><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status </span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Tahap Selesai:</span> </p><p>Mengakibatkan 1 poin <span style=\"color: #99FFFF\">Cryo DMG</span> kepada Karakter yang terpengaruh. Jika <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Penggunaan</span> hanya tersisa 1 dan Karakter terpengaruh <span style=\"color: #99FFFF\">Cryo</span>, maka DMG kali ini +1.</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Penggunaan: 2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/14/15595270/54adbd6e0af44cff009737afb67b0409_6382139910314624928.png",
                "id": "talent37606",
                "key": "Framing: Freezing Point Composition",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Framing: Freezing Point Composition"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 1 poin <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo DMG</span>, memulihkan 1 poin HP seluruh Karaktermu, dan memanggil <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Newsflash Field</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/14/15595270/d1cf9afd3481f21b5ec894c5c65557fe_6270095273000642569.png",
                "id": "talent92759",
                "key": "Still Photo: Comprehensive Confirmation",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Still Photo: Comprehensive Confirmation"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Panggilan</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Tahap Selesai:</span> Mengakibatkan 1 poin <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo DMG</span> dan memulihkan 1 poin HP Karakter Aktifmu.</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Penggunaan: 2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/18/15595270/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_4220508692474938372.png",
                "id": "talent334",
                "key": "Newsflash Field",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/18/15595270/3ab60df4ef6812b4db37e62ef3338cfe_1031297898527945182.png",
                "title": "Newsflash Field"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Memberikan Cryo dan dapat memicu Reaksi Elemental berikut:</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Melt</span>: DMG +2 poin untuk kasus ini<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Superconduct</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, mengakibatkan 1 Piercing DMG kepada seluruh Karakter lawan selain daripada target</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Frozen</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, target tidak dapat melangkah di Ronde ini (Dapat dihapus di muka setelah target menerima Physical DMG atau Pyro DMG, namun DMG +2)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/18/15595270/4bcc4b82a9d7ee22770f60afa54e9919_3216683594979447423.png",
                "id": "talent7243",
                "key": "Cryo DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Cryo DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Penggunaan</span></strong></p><p>Setelah efek kartu ini dipicu, 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan</span>-nya akan dikonsumsi.</p><p>Kartu ini akan langsung dibuang setelah semua <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan</span> telah dikonsumsi.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/18/15595270/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_8716377858765787875.png",
